  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li>neural net-based full-body VR solver</li><li>distinction of head and ribcage rotation</li><li>calculated elbow joint targets</li><li>calculated feet positions</li><li>body calibration</li><li>keeps accurate head and hands positions</li><li>supported locomotion from stick</li><li>input from scene components or default interface</li><li>special IK animation node for blending legs animation</li><li>can work with any VR headset ant motion controllers</li><li>source code is included</li></ul><p>Code Modules:</p><ul><li>VRIKBodyRuntime (Runtime)</li><li>VRIKBodyEditor (Editor)</li></ul><p>Number of Blueprints: 0</p><p>Number of C&#43;&#43; Classes: 3</p><p>Network Replicated: Yes</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: Win64, Linux</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms: Win64, Linux, Android (Quest)</p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v&#61;WQ98f0k2R60\" rel=\"nofollow\">VIDEO</a> | <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1iJrlW1h68bln6z18wN6_bDIR5csjilmm/view?usp&#61;share_link\" rel=\"nofollow\">PDF</a></p><p>Example Projects: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/14DmHL0Hr3cBJu9eZC2l_Nsk2bjgbHP18/view?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">5.2-5.4 for OpenXR</a> | <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1j2Fp3QiCerzLzUueh1_ACX8mY7dzVDEw/view?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">5.3-5.4 for MetaXR (Quest)</a></p><p>Executable Demo: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GuKCxeLQkyxtZNUSebwMzRGHq1eT4NMb/view?usp&#61;share_link\" rel=\"nofollow\">ZIP</a></p>",
